{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket: close イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\"><code>send()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>close</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>close</code> イベントは、 <code>WebSocket</code> の接続が閉じられたときに発生します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<p>イベント名を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> などのメソッドで使用するか、イベントハンドラープロパティを設定するかしてください。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'close'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclose</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベント型","title":"イベント型","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent\"><code>CloseEvent</code></a> です。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> から継承しています。</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Event\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"80\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"145\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      CloseEvent\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベントプロパティ","title":"イベントプロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>下記に示したプロパティに加えて、親インターフェイスである <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> からのプロパティが利用できます。</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"code\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent/code\" title=\"code\"><code>code</code></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>サーバーが送信したクローズコードを <code>unsigned short</code> で返します。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"reason\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent/reason\" title=\"reason\"><code>reason</code></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>サーバーが接続を閉じた理由を示す <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> を返します。これは、特定のサーバーとサブプロトコルに固有のものです。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"wasclean\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent/wasClean\" title=\"wasClean\"><code>wasClean</code></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>接続がきれいに閉じられたか否かを示す論理値を返します。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>接続が閉じられる時が分かれば、 UI を更新させたり、閉じた接続についてのデータを保存したりすることができます。以下の例では <code>exampleSocket</code> と呼ばれる変数が開かれた <code>WebSocket</code> を参照しており、このハンドラーが、ソケットが閉じられた場面を扱います。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>exampleSocket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'close'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The connection has been closed successfully.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>同じことを、イベントハンドラープロパティを用いて行うこともできます。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>exampleSocket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclose</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The connection has been closed successfully.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-close","title":"HTML Standard"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#handler-websocket-onclose","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.WebSocket.close_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.close_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\">WebSocket: error イベント</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\">WebSocket: message イベント</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\">WebSocket: open イベント</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\">WebSocket クライアントアプリケーションを書く</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"イベント型","id":"イベント型"},{"text":"イベントプロパティ","id":"イベントプロパティ"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"close イベントは、 WebSocket の接続が閉じられたときに発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket: close event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"close","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WebSocket : évènement close","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket.onclose","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/websocket/close_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/websocket/close_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","title":"WebSocket"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event","title":"WebSocket: close イベント"}],"pageTitle":"WebSocket: close イベント - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}